title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Salvage Yard Robbery Targets
content: Check in at your Salvage Yard to scope out this week’s robbery targets: the Benefactor LM87 (Super), Invetero Coquette BlackFin (Muscle), and Bravado Greenwood (Muscle). Select your target on the Salvage Yard’s planning computer and then get all the details on the operation via the planning wall.
